The Nigerian Air Force on Sunday announced that one of its airmen,
Corporal Meshach Iliya Komo, has died in a parachuting accident in
Kaduna.
The Airman who died on Sunday was undergoing recurrence training. His
death was announced in a statement by the Air Force Spokesman, Air
Commodore Ibikunle Daramola. The Force regretted that ugly incident.

			
